# Distrobox Generate Entry Background Apps

This file implements support for freedesktop background apps portal integration as an enhancement for issue #1964 related to background/tray icon integration.

## Implementation Overview

The integration will allow seamless interaction with background applications within the Distrobox environment, enabling tray icons and background processes management through the FreeDesktop portals.

## Benefits
- Enhanced user experience with background applications.
- Better integration with desktop environment features.
- Streamlined access to background functionalities.

## Usage
Ensure that the relevant background apps are registered and configured properly within Distrobox to take advantage of this integration.

## Future Work
Further enhancements could include support for additional portal features and improved user notifications.

---

This enhancement is part of ongoing efforts to improve the Distrobox experience and user interaction with background services.